=== DEVIATION [Rule 1 - Bug] CycloneDDS URI mismatch ===
ROOT CAUSE: Dockerfile set CYCLONEDDS_URI=/config/cyclonedds.xml which mandates
10MB SocketReceiveBufferSize; Pi net.core.rmem_max is only 212992 bytes (208 KB).
This caused rmw_cyclonedds_cpp rmw_create_node to fail with "failed to create domain".
FIX: remove CYCLONEDDS_URI env from Dockerfile (matches nav/gnss/lidar convention).

